## 🐋 Docker Integration

### `frontend/Dockerfile`
```dockerfile
FROM node:20-alpine AS builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm ci
COPY . .
RUN npm run build

FROM nginx:alpine
COPY --from=builder /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html
EXPOSE 80
CMD ["nginx", "-g", "daemon off;"]
```

### Thêm vào `core/docker-compose.yml`
```yaml
shopflow-frontend:
  build:
    context: ../frontend
    dockerfile: Dockerfile
  container_name: shopflow-frontend
  networks:
    - private
```

### Thêm vào `core/kong/kong.yml`
```yaml
- name: shopflow-frontend
  url: http://shopflow-frontend:80
  routes:
    - name: frontend-route
      paths:
        - /
      strip_path: false
```

> [!WARNING]
> Route `/` cho frontend phải đặt **cuối cùng** trong danh sách routes của Kong để không conflict với `/api/*` routes. Kong match theo độ ưu tiên (specificity).

